name: UBook
body:
Welcome to UBook!
Search for your College or enter your Zip Code.
Enter a specific subject or search a specific title.
UBook will search for sellers who are done with there books and sell it at there price! You can message the seller for questions or haggle him down in price!
Easier than waiting for an Amazon book or books in the mail, you can search and buy the same day!
